nodes.bodyText:
@MaryamZi Sorry I forgot pass this piece of information.
We need to do semantic validation for isolated-module-non-init-var-decl.
For example in following scenario we don't log an error in parser,
isolated final object{ }  obj;
But in the other scenarios we were forced to validate at parser as it could be a part of the immediate type descriptor.

